commit.message:
system.h (STRUCT_VALUE_INCOMING_REGNUM): Poison.

	* system.h (STRUCT_VALUE_INCOMING_REGNUM): Poison.
	* targhooks.c (default_struct_value_rtx): Don't use
	STRUCT_VALUE_INCOMING_REGNUM.

From-SVN: r75905

files.patch:

+
+	* system.h (STRUCT_VALUE_INCOMING_REGNUM): Poison.
+	* targhooks.c (default_struct_value_rtx): Don't use
+	STRUCT_VALUE_INCOMING_REGNUM.

 2004-01-15  Kelley Cook  <kcook@gcc.gnu.org>
